lead_paragraph: Rubby De La Rosa took a shutout into the eighth before running out of steam, Paul Goldschmidt homered and the Arizona Diamondbacks won their fifth straight game by beating the Colorado Rockies 5-1 on Tuesday night.

headline.print_headline: De La Rosa Sharp, Arizona Beats Rockies 5-1 for 5th Straight
